33:16.800 --> 33:17.994
Have this bottle.

33:19.040 --> 33:20.029
Here!

33:20.280 --> 33:21.269
C'mon, take it!

33:29.920 --> 33:32.229
Was that confetti?

33:32.520 --> 33:35.159
Guys, I've battled
with this mindset for years.

33:35.320 --> 33:37.515
I don't get
what makes people think...

33:37.680 --> 33:40.353
There's big money
in selling appliances.

33:40.520 --> 33:42.556
Look, Abdullah Abi.
Ogün's there. Ogün, Ogün!

33:42.840 --> 33:44.239
Throw the ball, c'mon!

33:44.440 --> 33:45.759
C'mon, boys. C'mon.

33:46.120 --> 33:48.998
Ali. Sami.
Let's hear it!

33:50.400 --> 33:53.039
Look, it's your duty to help Tank.

33:53.200 --> 33:55.839
We're boys from the same village.
Don't let me down.

33:55.920 --> 33:57.478
Look at all those fridges.

33:57.600 --> 34:00.433
