This one, say.

34:08.080 --> 34:10.310
Hey, Fikret.
Fikret, stop! Hey!

34:10.639 --> 34:11.914
Don't you do gas deliveries?

34:13.159 --> 34:15.196
- Yes.
- Are all the gas bottles yours?

34:15.280 --> 34:16.235
Yes.

34:16.400 --> 34:17.594
Who else's?

34:17.760 --> 34:18.909
Çeto, what's he saying?

34:19.080 --> 34:20.831
I'd sell someone else's gas?

34:22.199 --> 34:23.155
For God's sake.

34:23.320 --> 34:25.231
What's he saying?
F*ck your gas bottle!

34:25.480 --> 34:26.594
Fikret Abi,
what's with you?

34:26.760 --> 34:27.954
The catalogue.

34:28.880 --> 34:31.393
Here's the cost price of everything.

34:31.920 --> 34:33.638
OK? I sell the stuff.

34:33.920 --> 34:37.275
I pay the cost price plus my costs.
It's not my stuff!

34:37.679 --> 34:40.717
Saffet, you're an educated guy.
Please explain!

34:40.960 --> 34:42.678
I'll do my best then.

34:43.480 --> 34:44.674
Friends...

34:45.440 --> 34:47.271
It isn't his stuff.
That's that.

34:47.560 --> 34:48.993
Don't blame him,
he's a worker.

34:49.080 --> 34:52.197
Thanks, teacher.
Nothing beats an educated man.

34:54.199 --> 34:55.188
Give us an oven.

34:55.400 --> 34:56.435
Yes, an oven.

34:56.760 --> 35:00.230
If the fridges aren't yours,
we at least deserve an oven, Zeki.

35:00.560 --> 35:02.471
My blood pressure's shooting up.

35:02.880 --> 35:03.800
It's ours.

35:03.800 --> 35:06.109
Toraman.
We have to get something.

35:11.600 --> 35:13.033
This sucks.

35:13.520 --> 35:16.557
A whole day of arm-twisting
and look what we end up with.

35:16.800 --> 35:18.074
Home bread won't even fit.

35:18.280 --> 35:20.555
A toaster will get us nowhere.

35:20.720 --> 35:23.439
Just to reiterate,
it's not the man's stuff.

35:23.720 --> 35:26.837
- He just gets a cut.
- Right. It's all your fault.

35:27.040 --> 35:29.508
We got the point,
but pretended not to.

35:29.600 --> 35:31.397
You and your wise-guy trips.

35:31.560 --> 35:33.790
He's a teacher, right?
He's educated.

35:33.960 --> 35:37.032
So our Zeki revs him up
and he goes for it.

35:37.160 --> 35:38.912
Where's Emel, huh?
Where's Emel Sayýn?

35:39.320 --> 35:40.719
Where's Emel Sayýn?

35:40.920 --> 35:42.433
