01:19:19.000 --> 01:19:20.115
What a great guy!

01:19:20.200 --> 01:19:22.475
Brother! My brother!
You're the best!

01:19:23.960 --> 01:19:25.109
What are you doing?

01:19:25.480 --> 01:19:28.916
Behave! What will they think of you?
For heaven’s sake!

01:19:30.760 --> 01:19:31.715
Oh my!

01:19:32.440 --> 01:19:34.032
Did we call the gendarmes?

01:19:34.200 --> 01:19:35.474
I should've run for it.

01:19:35.920 --> 01:19:37.069
You think they realized?

01:19:37.200 --> 01:19:38.918
Do they know
Ýshak Amca's dead?

01:19:39.080 --> 01:19:40.752
- Welcome.
- Thanks.

01:19:41.040 --> 01:19:43.429
- Welcome.
- Are you the wedding hosts?

01:19:43.760 --> 01:19:44.875
Yes, that's us.

01:19:45.280 --> 01:19:46.269
There's a problem.

01:19:46.520 --> 01:19:47.509
What's that?

01:19:51.960 --> 01:19:53.518
The gendarmes mustn't come in here.

01:19:53.800 --> 01:19:55.119
If they do,
they mustn't see.

01:19:55.400 --> 01:19:57.550
If they see,
I'll shoot the lot.

01:19:57.960 --> 01:20:00.520
- I'll walk away and not...
- Abi, please.

01:20:02.520 --> 01:20:07.116
- Rear sight, eye...
- No glasses. I dropped my glasses.

01:20:07.800 --> 01:20:09.950
I'll show you glasses.
Move! Go!

01:20:10.440 --> 01:20:13.512
The kids nabbed the money
off the floor and went spending.

01:20:13.720 --> 01:20:16.188
Why would we have fake money,
commander?

01:20:16.520 --> 01:20:17.873
We need to search the guests.

01:20:18.120 --> 01:20:20.680
You can't! Tongues will wag.
How do we explain?

01:20:21.160 --> 01:20:26.234
They'll say we called you in
to search everyone for wedding loot.

01:20:26.720 --> 01:20:30.076
You found it on the dance floor.
The money is Çeto's. C'mon!

01:20:43.760 --> 01:20:44.875
Yes, it's mine.

01:20:45.600 --> 01:20:48.672
Search me. Let's go, commander.
Can't run from justice.

01:20:49.280 --> 01:20:52.033
- What are you doing?
- Helping justice, Fikret Abi.

01:20:53.000 --> 01:20:55.389
Which means?
I'll do my punishment.

01:20:55.800 --> 01:20:57.552
So the wedding won't break up.

01:20:57.840 --> 01:21:01.071
Fikret Abi, the wedding's over to you.
Have a great time.

01:21:01.280 --> 01:21:03.635
Look at Çetin.
Talk about selfless.

01:21:03.840 --> 01:21:07.150
Asshole, run off and dump me
with the crap. You owe me.

01:21:14.840 --> 01:21:17.513
Where's the registrar?
Let's get this thing over.

01:21:17.760 --> 01:21:18.875
How did the guy die?

01:21:19.320 --> 01:21:21.675
That's the main thing.
Çeto said he had cake.

01:21:22.040 --> 01:21:25.874
What if he got poisoned by the cake?
What if all the guests die?

01:21:26.400 --> 01:21:29.676
- Should we cancel the thing?
- It's almost over, Fikret Abi.

01:21:31.840 --> 01:21:33.273
It may be a sign from above.

01:21:33.360 --> 01:21:36.557
For God's sake, when did you ever
care about signs from above?

01:21:36.840 --> 01:21:39.559
- I'm screwed and you just dump me!
- But look at us!

01:21:39.920 --> 01:21:43.356
If my parents hear about the loan,
they'll disown me.

01:21:44.760 --> 01:21:49.276
This wedding has to go on for me,
for Saffet, the village teacher!

01:21:49.480 --> 01:21:50.708
Hey, OK. Relax.

01:21:51.000 --> 01:21:52.194
The wedding goes on.

01:21:55.480 --> 01:21:56.708
Don't get upset.
C'mon.

01:21:57.720 --> 01:21:59.711
Follow me.
Saffet, follow me.

01:22:08.840 --> 01:22:10.990
Tell Tank some fib.
We're going.

01:22:11.080 --> 01:22:12.559
What's up, honey?

01:22:12.640 --> 01:22:15.757
Tarik, we're just off to the bathroom.
We'll be right back.

01:22:15.880 --> 01:22:16.869
Sure, go ahead.

01:22:16.920 --> 01:22:21.277
But don't be long, honey.
The registrar will be here any minute.

01:22:22.680 --> 01:22:24.272
- What's going on?
- LADIES

01:22:35.600 --> 01:22:37.591
Your guy's here, in Sivas.

01:22:38.880 --> 01:22:41.269
Don't you hear me?
Say something!

01:22:41.480 --> 01:22:44.313
They'll kill you!
Tank too, if you tell him.

01:22:44.400 --> 01:22:47.631
- What's happening to me?
- Let's escape through there, c'mon.

01:22:48.120 --> 01:22:51.476
If they don't find us,
no one will get hurt.

01:23:00.520 --> 01:23:03.239
- Selam aleykum.
- Aleykum selam, son.

01:23:03.440 --> 01:23:06.159
- How's the cake?
- A bit too much cream perhaps.

01:23:06.480 --> 01:23:10.632
- Praise the Lord! How are you, son?
- Fine, thanks. I'm well.

01:23:10.800 --> 01:23:12.472
Have you seen Ýshak, son?

01:23:12.600 --> 01:23:14.875
Ýshak Amca?
Yes. Yes. Yes, I did.

01:23:15.320 --> 01:23:17.151
Just now, dancing.

01:23:18.000 --> 01:23:20.275
He seemed a bit dazed.
Huh, Teyze?

01:23:20.480 --> 01:23:24.029
- I wonder if something's wrong?
- No, what could be wrong?

01:23:24.200 --> 01:23:25.474
I don't know.

01:23:25.680 --> 01:23:27.875
He seemed a bit pale.
He had no color.

01:23:28.000 --> 01:23:31.470
It's the light, dear.
His cholesterol's OK, no diabetes.

01:23:31.800 --> 01:23:33.119
- His heart?
- What's the matter?

01:23:33.280 --> 01:23:35.111
Did he have heart problems?

01:23:35.360 --> 01:23:36.793
Not even tooth decay.

01:23:36.960 --> 01:23:40.873
I have a bad heart, blood sugar,
blood pressure problems, everything.

01:23:41.120 --> 01:23:45.318
But Ýshak is fit as a fiddle.
He eats so much though.

01:23:46.000 --> 01:23:47.672
Eating a lot is OK.

01:23:48.320 --> 01:23:50.072
Did he have
silent heart disease?

01:23:50.360 --> 01:23:51.679
The kind that...

01:23:51.800 --> 01:23:53.870
I can't keep quiet any longer.

01:23:54.000 --> 01:23:56.116
Be strong.
We've lost Ýshak Amca.

01:23:56.480 --> 01:23:59.916
He just dropped dead.
We carried him inside to avoid a fuss.

01:24:00.400 --> 01:24:04.234
Well, no use crying over spilled milk.
Be strong, Teyze.

01:24:04.560 --> 01:24:05.709
We're all upset.

01:24:05.880 --> 01:24:07.029
I cried.

01:24:07.960 --> 01:24:09.916
Everyone had tears in their eyes.

01:24:10.120 --> 01:24:12.554
Then the jewelry scam
to land 20,000 lira...

01:24:13.280 --> 01:24:14.235
Teyze!

01:24:15.400 --> 01:24:17.914
Lord, are You
putting us to the test?

01:24:21.240 --> 01:24:22.673
F*ck this, enough!

01:24:23.360 --> 01:24:25.749
OK, you're one of us.
On the way with the camel...

01:24:48.960 --> 01:24:50.029
Saffet!

01:24:53.040 --> 01:24:54.758
- Did you rat on us?
- What do you mean?

01:24:55.760 --> 01:24:57.637
I told Þengül Teyze everything.

01:24:57.760 --> 01:25:00.194
She knew most of it anyway.
Was it so bad?

01:25:00.440 --> 01:25:02.112
So what's she doing here?

01:25:02.360 --> 01:25:04.874
I was explaining things
and it just happened.

01:25:04.920 --> 01:25:06.239
She passed away.

01:25:06.360 --> 01:25:07.475
Passed away?

01:25:08.760 --> 01:25:10.796
She's dead?
So how did she die?

01:25:11.160 --> 01:25:13.515
Well, last thing she did
was eat cake.

01:25:13.600 --> 01:25:15.795
Çetin messed up the cake.
Where's Çetin?

01:25:16.400 --> 01:25:17.355
Çetin!

01:25:17.800 --> 01:25:20.109
- He's at the police station.
- Doing what?

01:25:20.480 --> 01:25:22.835
Umm, well...
He was kind of arrested.

01:25:24.120 --> 01:25:25.155
Çetin!

01:25:27.920 --> 01:25:29.148
The bridesmaid!

01:25:29.360 --> 01:25:30.679
Hand her over.

01:25:31.240 --> 01:25:32.275
Hold tight.

01:25:36.600 --> 01:25:37.555
What happened?

01:25:37.680 --> 01:25:39.511
Search me.
She talks weird.

01:25:39.760 --> 01:25:41.478
She kept babbling.
First I was quiet.

01:25:41.760 --> 01:25:45.275
She led me to the forest.
I showed my face and knocked her out.

01:25:45.480 --> 01:25:46.595
Her head’s bleeding.

01:25:46.760 --> 01:25:48.512
Þengül Teyze!
Why are you here?

01:25:48.640 --> 01:25:50.392
- She knows.
- I'll tell then.

01:25:50.560 --> 01:25:52.790
I had a hard time knocking her out.

01:25:52.920 --> 01:25:55.434
Blood's normal.
I hit her more than once.

01:25:56.280 --> 01:25:59.477
Oh God!
Oh my God!

01:26:00.160 --> 01:26:01.752
There's blood on my dress!

01:26:02.000 --> 01:26:04.673
My adorable dress!
What do we do, Þengül Teyze?

01:26:04.840 --> 01:26:07.070
Good heavens,
is it the color or what?

01:26:07.320 --> 01:26:09.914
You threw toy money at kids
to look rich?

01:26:10.160 --> 01:26:13.630
It's from being poor, commander.
I messed up so forgive me.

01:26:13.800 --> 01:26:15.870
I did my army service
as a gendarme.

01:26:16.640 --> 01:26:19.518
- You have a tough job.
- Where were you for army service?

01:26:19.640 --> 01:26:20.709
Here, in Sivas.

01:26:20.800 --> 01:26:24.156
I've been here 10 years
and never seen you. Which intake?

01:26:24.480 --> 01:26:27.199
Intake?
Commander, I have to answer this.

01:26:27.280 --> 01:26:29.919
Sorry, it may be important.
You know the story.

01:26:30.320 --> 01:26:31.309
Hello?

01:26:31.440 --> 01:26:34.750
- Çetin, where are you?
- At the gendarmerie, Mum. You know.

01:26:35.000 --> 01:26:35.955
Drop dead!

01:26:36.040 --> 01:26:37.075
Oh my God.

01:26:37.920 --> 01:26:40.718
OK, Mum,
but I'm in a fix right now.

01:26:40.840 --> 01:26:42.273
<i>Come back.
Make an excuse.</i>

01:26:42.400 --> 01:26:43.913
- Ishak's wife is dead too.
- My God!

01:26:44.080 --> 01:26:45.035
What happened?

01:26:45.160 --> 01:26:48.596
Yilmaz beat up the bride's friend.
The girl's face is a mess.

01:26:48.720 --> 01:26:51.678
The bridesmaid?
They tried suede, umm, you know.

01:26:51.840 --> 01:26:54.308
To knock her out!
Why would I beat her up?

01:26:54.440 --> 01:26:56.032
C'mon, come back fast.

01:26:57.480 --> 01:26:59.118
Oh, woe is me!

01:27:01.080 --> 01:27:02.593
Where were we?

01:27:05.160 --> 01:27:08.436
Commander, I just lied to you.
I didn't do army service.

01:27:08.600 --> 01:27:10.636
I said I did it here
to get sympathy.

01:27:10.760 --> 01:27:11.954
I'm a draft dodger.

01:27:12.120 --> 01:27:14.270
But I dodged flawlessly
for21 years.

01:27:14.560 --> 01:27:16.437
So today's the day.
Recruit me.

01:27:17.200 --> 01:27:20.351
What do you say?
Let me be of use to the nation.

01:27:21.680 --> 01:27:25.116
Why was the commander so mad?
All I did was confess.

01:27:25.800 --> 01:27:28.872
And take the piss?
Shame on you at your age!

01:27:29.160 --> 01:27:30.673
For heaven’s sake.

01:27:32.640 --> 01:27:34.232
Where did I put it?

01:27:35.440 --> 01:27:37.431
I wanted to ask you, youngst...

01:27:39.520 --> 01:27:41.397
We messed up.
Here, fire away.

01:27:41.480 --> 01:27:45.678
I was about to ask for a light.
So smoking does shorten your life.

01:27:45.760 --> 01:27:46.749
Explain, Fikret.

01:27:47.000 --> 01:27:48.752
The girl fell off the camel.

01:27:48.960 --> 01:27:51.076
The dress only fitted Yilmaz.
Go on.

01:27:51.320 --> 01:27:52.992
When Ýshak Amca dropped dead...

01:27:53.200 --> 01:27:56.476
You told his wife and she died.
Saffet told her for sure.

01:27:56.640 --> 01:27:59.154
Anyway you can't
bring back the dead. Go on.

01:27:59.240 --> 01:28:00.195
This girl?

01:28:00.320 --> 01:28:02.914
She found out who I was
so I hamstringed her.

01:28:03.080 --> 01:28:05.753
Are you Spider Man? Nut!
What's with the hands?

01:28:05.960 --> 01:28:09.509
I saw, heard and know nothing.
All I have is one son.

01:28:09.640 --> 01:28:11.835
It's his wedding.
I want no scenes.

01:28:12.000 --> 01:28:12.955
Fix this.

01:28:13.080 --> 01:28:17.596
I'm going to put on more lipstick.
Now fix this. For heaven's sake!

01:28:18.000 --> 01:28:19.069
Sharp lady.

01:28:19.480 --> 01:28:21.471
Learned to read in 4 days.
She's sharp.

01:28:33.720 --> 01:28:37.554
Where were you, honey?
The registrar's almost here.

01:28:40.400 --> 01:28:42.550
Marika, where's your man?

01:28:43.520 --> 01:28:48.116
Tank, is she upset with me?
Why won't she talk to me?

01:28:51.040 --> 01:28:52.234
Tarik, run!

01:28:52.960 --> 01:28:53.995
What's going on?

01:28:59.680 --> 01:29:00.795
Selam aleyküm.

01:29:01.280 --> 01:29:02.235
Hands off!

01:29:03.080 --> 01:29:03.990
Fikret.

01:29:04.240 --> 01:29:07.232
Who are you bashing,
f*cking paleface?

01:29:07.800 --> 01:29:08.994
Fikret.

01:29:11.880 --> 01:29:12.915
Saffet.

01:29:13.080 --> 01:29:15.594
Boy, does he bash!
Run!

01:29:16.200 --> 01:29:17.235
Asshole Saffet.

01:29:20.720 --> 01:29:23.359
F*ck it!
What is this?

01:29:24.480 --> 01:29:25.879
What's the scam?

01:29:25.960 --> 01:29:26.995
God, that's ugly.

01:29:27.480 --> 01:29:29.232
- What's going on?
- Who are those guys?

01:29:29.440 --> 01:29:32.034
Yilmaz Abi, how come
you're in the bride's dress?

01:29:32.160 --> 01:29:34.879
- You answer. Mine's a long story.
- Mine's longer.

01:29:35.120 --> 01:29:37.156
The camel snatched the bride.
She fell off and passed out.

01:29:37.360 --> 01:29:41.273
So I wore the dress. And we lost
your aunt and uncle. My condolences.

01:29:44.800 --> 01:29:46.552
The camel snatched the bride?

01:29:46.800 --> 01:29:49.473
Your uncle's dead
and you wait for the bride!

01:29:49.760 --> 01:29:52.479
Why are the guys chasing us?
What do they want?

01:29:52.960 --> 01:29:54.359
To kill us.

01:29:54.520 --> 01:29:56.556
They'll pump bullets
like perfume spray.

01:29:56.760 --> 01:30:01.117
Why didn't you say so from the start?
Run, man! Run!

01:30:01.280 --> 01:30:03.475
Ah, Marika!

01:30:04.040 --> 01:30:06.873
Þengül Teyze, I put Ýsmail Abi
and Fikret Abi in there.

01:30:07.120 --> 01:30:10.669
I told people drunk relatives had
kidnapped the groom, it's tradition.

01:30:10.880 --> 01:30:12.757
Otherwise they'd panic.

01:30:14.440 --> 01:30:15.873
God, in the name of God!

01:30:18.560 --> 01:30:19.709
Fikret Abi!

01:30:20.120 --> 01:30:21.633
Oh God, what did I do?

01:30:21.840 --> 01:30:24.308
Forgive me, God!

01:30:24.480 --> 01:30:26.516
Forgive me, God.
Fikret Abi.

01:30:26.840 --> 01:30:27.829
Ýsmail Abi.

01:30:27.960 --> 01:30:29.393
Oh my God, Ýsmail Abi!

01:30:29.960 --> 01:30:32.076
Ýsmail Abi!

01:30:32.240 --> 01:30:33.514
Abi, what did we do?

01:30:33.760 --> 01:30:36.558
Abi, what's happening?
Here, one last kiss.

01:30:36.920 --> 01:30:38.512
- Çetin Abi?
- Oh my God!

01:30:39.000 --> 01:30:41.275
- When did you get here?
- Just now.

01:30:41.440 --> 01:30:42.429
How did they die?

01:30:42.600 --> 01:30:44.750
Those girls came here from Latvia
to die?

01:30:45.080 --> 01:30:48.959
<i>- It was the cake, wasn't it?
- They aren't dead, just passed out.</i>

01:30:49.240 --> 01:30:50.798
- The bridesmaid?
- Passed out too.

01:30:50.880 --> 01:30:51.949
Ýshak Amca and his wife?

01:30:52.360 --> 01:30:53.395
They're dead.

01:30:53.760 --> 01:30:56.115
Are you stoned?
You hauled him here alone.

01:30:58.560 --> 01:31:00.596
Who beat them up?

01:31:04.560 --> 01:31:06.437
We're finished, Tank.

01:31:07.040 --> 01:31:09.679
I never thought of my dress
as a burial shroud.

01:31:10.480 --> 01:31:11.515
Abi, what do we do?

01:31:12.120 --> 01:31:13.189
I hear noises.

01:31:13.400 --> 01:31:14.469
They're coming.

01:31:14.600 --> 01:31:16.113
We have to run, Tank.
Run!

01:31:16.360 --> 01:31:17.679
Wait. Hold it.

01:31:18.680 --> 01:31:19.829
Where's a rock?

01:31:26.360 --> 01:31:27.349
I set up a decoy.

01:31:27.520 --> 01:31:29.033
C'mon, up the tree.

01:31:29.400 --> 01:31:32.437
- They're coming, Tank. Quick.
- I'll hold the train then.

01:31:32.720 --> 01:31:33.948
No need.

01:31:34.040 --> 01:31:35.837
If only I'd gone up first.

01:31:48.720 --> 01:31:50.233
Oof! That was him jumping!

01:31:50.680 --> 01:31:52.352
Man, who are these guys?

01:31:57.720 --> 01:32:00.598
You know, if you'd been friends
it would've been handy.

01:32:00.680 --> 01:32:03.194
Abi, don't look,
but they're looking at us.

01:32:03.680 --> 01:32:05.238
- What did he say?
- Come down.

01:32:07.400 --> 01:32:08.594
What did you say?

01:32:08.800 --> 01:32:09.789
I said...

01:32:10.440 --> 01:32:12.795
What's going on?
It's the devil!

01:32:17.040 --> 01:32:20.715
Yilmaz Abi, I said,
"Come get us yourself if you can".

01:32:20.760 --> 01:32:22.557
I see.
No need.

01:32:23.120 --> 01:32:25.554
Hey!
So you decide!

01:32:26.280 --> 01:32:30.319
40 mules, 40 cleavers
or 40 cm of shlong?

01:32:30.680 --> 01:32:35.708
They don't know Turkish. You translate.
No wait, I'll translate them to hell!

01:33:29.480 --> 01:33:31.118
Am I early?
Where is everyone?

01:33:31.200 --> 01:33:32.713
Come here.
C'mon, come here!

01:33:34.000 --> 01:33:37.834
It's all your fault! Asshole!
If you'd come 1 hour earlier.

01:33:37.960 --> 01:33:40.394
You know how many people are dead?

01:33:40.760 --> 01:33:43.194
- A camel ran out in front of me.
- So?

01:33:43.880 --> 01:33:47.111
- I swerved and crashed into a tree.
- Fucker!

01:33:49.200 --> 01:33:52.158
Come here.
You're fucked.

01:33:52.960 --> 01:33:53.949
You too!

01:33:54.680 --> 01:33:55.795
And you!

01:33:55.920 --> 01:33:58.309
And you!
And you!

01:34:00.240 --> 01:34:03.198
All except you, blondie.
Now you...

01:34:09.240 --> 01:34:10.559
OK, let go.
Let go.

01:34:15.960 --> 01:34:17.552
Take a look and sign.

01:34:18.200 --> 01:34:21.431
It was my first time back in years.
And only for you.

01:34:21.560 --> 01:34:24.600
<i>It's not the place you miss
but the people in it.</i>

01:34:24.600 --> 01:34:27.068
<i>Fikret Abi gets fired up
faster than you ever saw.</i>

01:34:27.200 --> 01:34:30.272
<i>We went on ahead.
I fixed the fuses and put them back.</i>

01:34:32.920 --> 01:34:36.230
You almost did it, kiddo.
Bad luck, that's all.

01:34:36.520 --> 01:34:39.080
- Çetin Abi, please. Not now.
- You're right.

01:34:40.840 --> 01:34:42.319
He shoots
and it's a goal!

01:34:42.480 --> 01:34:45.074
Çeto, please.
It's not the time or place.

01:34:45.240 --> 01:34:46.275
You're right.

01:34:50.560 --> 01:34:54.838
He had a dickey heart, kept it quiet.
A silent heart thing.

01:34:55.320 --> 01:34:58.392
And his wife,
she was sick from head to toe.

01:34:58.520 --> 01:35:00.750
They both passed on together.

01:35:01.120 --> 01:35:02.997
Nurten had twins last night.

01:35:03.280 --> 01:35:05.794
She's called one Ýshak,
the other Hamiyet.

01:35:05.960 --> 01:35:09.714
True, they're girls, so one
gets a raw deal. But that's life.

01:35:10.240 --> 01:35:12.037
I'm not laughing!

01:35:12.440 --> 01:35:13.555
No, no.

01:35:13.800 --> 01:35:15.995
So you snatched the girl, huh?

01:35:16.560 --> 01:35:17.993
Let's say we ran away.

01:35:18.680 --> 01:35:21.433
It was her fiancé
who beat your poor dad, huh?

01:35:21.720 --> 01:35:23.073
Yes, Abi.

01:35:25.080 --> 01:35:27.674
So the girl having no family etc was...

01:35:27.800 --> 01:35:29.119
- Lies too, Abi.
- Right?

01:35:29.880 --> 01:35:33.270
Tarik, did you really
finish college?

01:35:33.760 --> 01:35:35.637
- Yes, Dad.
- Phew.

01:35:37.440 --> 01:35:38.714
But I didn't do a master's.

01:35:39.200 --> 01:35:41.839
I lied when college
dragged on for2 years.

01:35:42.160 --> 01:35:43.149
Good for you.

01:35:43.320 --> 01:35:46.756
Pity my glasses, not him.
They were my only reminder of Dad.

01:35:47.080 --> 01:35:49.833
Please say something
before I lunge at him.

01:35:51.000 --> 01:35:52.194
Tank.

01:35:53.000 --> 01:35:56.709
Come outside with me.
We don't want a scene during prayers.

01:36:03.400 --> 01:36:05.994
- Did you trip him, Fikret Abi?
- Yes.

01:36:08.960 --> 01:36:10.188
Now look, Tank.

01:36:10.320 --> 01:36:15.348
A real father has his son circumcised,
sends him to school and the army...

01:36:15.840 --> 01:36:16.875
Then does his wedding.
That's our way.

01:36:16.920 --> 01:36:21.357
I won't have this village accuse me
of not giving my son a wedding!

01:36:21.760 --> 01:36:26.072
Home's become a house of mourning.
We can't do jollity for a while.

01:36:26.720 --> 01:36:27.948
It would be wrong.

01:36:29.400 --> 01:36:32.073
Now here.
The keys to the car.

01:36:33.240 --> 01:36:34.719
What car?

01:36:36.360 --> 01:36:37.554
Yilmaz's.

01:36:38.040 --> 01:36:41.880
I offered him a spare
but he said he'd get it working.

01:36:41.880 --> 01:36:44.519
He's a professional.
And a man of his word.

01:36:44.680 --> 01:36:47.114
He's so like my late dad.

01:36:48.960 --> 01:36:51.520
Hey, don't translate that!

01:36:51.760 --> 01:36:56.790
Here. These are your plane tickets.
And this is what's left of the money.

01:36:59.040 --> 01:37:01.315
Spend it on the wedding, OK?

01:37:01.640 --> 01:37:04.200
But don't put in
any money of your own.

01:37:04.840 --> 01:37:06.910
Only spend that much
on the wedding.

01:37:07.560 --> 01:37:10.438
Wait a second, Dad.
I'm lost. Markus and co?

01:37:10.680 --> 01:37:13.911
You know Çetin Abi.
He's a bit slow.

01:37:14.080 --> 01:37:17.709
When there's a fight
he's an Ottoman routing the infidel.

01:37:18.080 --> 01:37:21.868
So when he found out
they were real infidels, he showed off.

01:37:22.200 --> 01:37:26.637
The doctor said
he'd pounded them like animals.

01:37:26.840 --> 01:37:31.789
Markus and co will be on baby food
fora while. They can't chew.

01:37:32.160 --> 01:37:36.551
They still have all their teeth,
but the mechanism is kaput.

01:37:36.840 --> 01:37:39.195
Dad, you are a true man.

01:37:39.320 --> 01:37:40.389
Come here.

01:37:41.360 --> 01:37:43.430
- Thanks a lot.
- Take care.

01:37:46.840 --> 01:37:50.230
Don't worry about the others.
I'll fudge something...

01:37:50.640 --> 01:37:54.758
And find a way to explain.
Don't you worry. Now off you go.

01:38:00.520 --> 01:38:04.638
C'mon, out. You aren't needed now.
Out, c'mon. I'll translate.

01:38:08.040 --> 01:38:09.359
OK, see you!

01:38:13.720 --> 01:38:15.551
3 YEARS LATER
ISTANBUL

01:38:15.720 --> 01:38:18.314
Emel! Emel! Emel!

01:38:19.360 --> 01:38:20.429
Emel.

01:38:20.520 --> 01:38:21.714
- Sayýn.
- Haným.

01:38:21.800 --> 01:38:23.074
- Emel Sayýn Haným!
- Saffet?

01:38:23.320 --> 01:38:24.309
Emel Abla.

01:38:24.480 --> 01:38:27.392
Saffet, I don't believe it!
Dearest!

01:38:27.480 --> 01:38:28.993
Where have you been?

01:38:29.200 --> 01:38:31.316
You never call
to ask how I am.

01:38:31.440 --> 01:38:34.238
I called a ton of times.
Aren't you family?

01:38:34.920 --> 01:38:37.992
I was gonna ask if you'd come
for Ýsmail Abi's wedding in Sivas.

01:38:38.040 --> 01:38:40.076
Of course I'd have come, Saffet.

01:38:42.760 --> 01:38:45.194
It's OK, Emel Haným.
Don't worry.

01:38:45.440 --> 01:38:48.352
The couple married in Latvia.
They work in Istanbul now.

01:38:48.600 --> 01:38:50.556
And they had a son.
I'm Fikret.

01:38:51.000 --> 01:38:53.275
Saffet is like a son
and Sivas my sun.

01:38:53.520 --> 01:38:56.478
- Thanks, Fikret.
- Emel Haným, let me take those hands.

01:38:56.720 --> 01:39:00.793
Forgive my friends for being weird.
It's the first time they saw a star.

01:39:01.120 --> 01:39:03.395
Ýsmail Abi says it's a tradition.

01:39:03.520 --> 01:39:05.909
With us it's granddads
who handle circumcision dos.

01:39:06.120 --> 01:39:07.269
That's how we were taught.

01:39:07.400 --> 01:39:11.712
So our youngster has his circumcision.
You'll come sing a song, won't you?

01:39:11.920 --> 01:39:14.275
And that way
you'll make up with Saffet.

01:39:14.440 --> 01:39:16.237
Of course I'll come.

01:39:16.760 --> 01:39:18.876
I'll be there.
So when is it?

01:39:19.120 --> 01:39:20.269
When, Abi?

01:39:20.640 --> 01:39:21.914
Soon.
